dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kevin Kelly. May I have your name, please?
Hi Kevin, my name is Beverly Hill.
Nice to meet you, Beverly. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes, using individual digits?
Sure, my policy number is eight four zero zero five one.
Thank you. Could you also confirm the make and model of your primary vehicle, specifying each digit separately for clarity?
The vehicle is a two zero one eight Honda Accord.
Great, thank you for the information, Beverly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you, Kevin.
You're welcome, Beverly. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a wonderful day!
